00:35:14,492 --> 00:35:15,636
Dan Oh.

506
00:35:35,881 --> 00:35:37,057
Haru.

507
00:35:38,112 --> 00:35:39,286
Haru.

508
00:35:40,282 --> 00:35:41,656
Haru.

509
00:35:42,552 --> 00:35:44,297
Haru...

