531
00:37:43,102 --> 00:37:44,702
- What?
- Erase that.

532
00:37:44,702 --> 00:37:46,041
Who are you to order us around?

533
00:37:46,041 --> 00:37:47,312
Me?

534
00:37:47,312 --> 00:37:50,356
